This Target Application will allow Target to 

- Advertise exclusive instore group or individual based deals to customers within the store or nearby area that have the Target app. 
- Allow for a geo-location chat feature to enable customers to interact with one another in any group deal collaboration
- Allow customers to share their deals with friends on social media sites such as twitter, facebook and pinterest to promote a deal and better market the target brand
- Allow customers to scan upto x amount of scans of products to show interest in buying an item then based of certain conditions met 
